  keywords    = {AIDS-Related Opportunistic Infections, epidemiology/immunology/microbiology; Computer Simulation; Disease Outbreaks; Disease Progression; HIV Infections, complications; Models, Theoretical; Mycobacterium tuberculosis, genetics/immunology; Risk Assessment; Tuberculosis, Multidrug-Resistant, complications/epidemiology/immunology/transmission},
