  keywords    = {Antitubercular Agents, therapeutic use; Drug Resistance, Multiple; Humans; Isoniazid, therapeutic use; Models, Theoretical; Practice Guidelines as Topic; Rifampin, therapeutic use; Tuberculosis, Pulmonary, drug therapy/prevention /&/ control; World Health Organization},
